### How to use — quick
1. Open the HTML file in your phone browser.  
2. Tap **Choose Image**, pick an image. The image appears on canvas.  
3. Tap the image to sample a color (or use the color picker). Select multiple colors if needed.  
4. Adjust **Shade Tolerance**, **Simplify**, **Smooth Level**, **Smart Suggest opacity/dash**.  
5. Use **Process** to create suggested cut shapes (they appear as gray overlays with dashed outlines).  
6. Accept any suggested object(s) you want (click accept on the suggestion). You can also manually select masks, merge them, or remove pieces.  
7. Export: **Download SVG** or **Download PNG** (select background white/transparent).  
8. Everything saved directly to your device.

